item.name: Golden Rice Ball
item.detail:
"Event BP Recovery Item"
Obtained during "The Demonic Capital: Rashomon."
A golden rice ball fit for the truly golden one.
Curry-flavored, but mild.
When you eat it, it will make your waist light up, turn your brocade into bamboo grass, or even make your tuft look like a girl's, but only if made with Japanese rice...
Just what type of rice is this?
Recovers 8 BP during the Rashomon Raids.

item.name: Rice Ball of Power
item.detail:
"Event BP Recovery Item"
Obtained during "The Demonic Capital: Rashomon."
A rice ball that represents the friendship with the animals of Mt. Ashigara.
Power will pour out of your body with just one bite!
"I'm totally pumped with motivation!"
That was the review of a Rider passing by.
Recovers 2 BP during the Rashomon Raids.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Welcome. Fufu, to think I would open up a shop like this... Oh, how ridiculous.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 2
voiceLines.subtitle: For you who has come from afar, welcome. Would you like some tea? Take your time and look around, I've got plenty in this shop. You might just find something you want.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 3
voiceLines.subtitle: I don't recommend holding back for too long. Either you release everything you bottled up, or you hold it for even longer... Don't be embarassed, if you have something that's troubling you, I will take a look for you here.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 11
voiceLines.subtitle: This is it, time to close the shop. These will just rot away if I keep them, so make sure you exchange them all, okay?

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 12
voiceLines.subtitle: For the prize exchange, you already finished everything to the last drop? Did you leave anything?

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 13
voiceLines.subtitle: Fufufu, make sure you squeeze out everything and have no leftovers. Exchange all the prizes, okay?

voiceLines.name: About the Event 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Welcome. Don't hold back, take whatever you want. Good business makes me happy too.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 2
voiceLines.subtitle: Completely, completely... A good word, is it not? I have to suck it all out, down to the marrow of the bones.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 3
voiceLines.subtitle: You don't have to hold back when you're with me. All your desires are cute to an oni like me.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 4
voiceLines.subtitle: You should check all notices carefully. The worst things in this fleeting life are expirations and contracts. Even I don't want to meet a bill collector.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 5
voiceLines.subtitle: Don't look at me like that. You'll make me blush. If I'm what you want most, then you have strange tastes, Master.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 6
voiceLines.subtitle:
It seems the party is over.
Please exchange your gifts while you can. Don't leave any leftovers. Bye, bye.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 7
voiceLines.subtitle: Oh sweetie, aren't you a popular one. I wonder if you will visit me again tomorrow? That aside, how many times have you come to me today already?

voiceLines.name: About the Event 8
voiceLines.subtitle: Yes? You came here to see me? That makes me so happy. You know, I really wanted to see you as well... Just kidding. Fufu, that's just a joke.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 9
voiceLines.subtitle: How are you doing? No, I can tell by looking at your face, you don't have to tell me. Do your best out there.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 10
voiceLines.subtitle: It's not good to get too enthralled by one thing but... you... are trying your best to see me right? Fufufu, in that case I can't really stop you now, can I?

voiceLines.name: About the Event 11
voiceLines.subtitle: Sweetie, the depths of your desire, I want to see more of it. Can you show me? ...Pretty please?

voiceLines.name: About the Event 12
voiceLines.subtitle: We're done, that's it. Make sure you grab whatever you need, and relax both your body and mind before you leave.

voiceLines.name: About the Event 13
voiceLines.subtitle:
I guess this is goodbye. Don't forget about me, okay, Sweetie?
I'm going to miss you... Just kidding, fufufu. If fate allows, we'll see each other again.

voiceLines.name: About the Mission 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Congratulations. Here, why don't you take this reward with you.

voiceLines.name: About the Mission 2
voiceLines.subtitle: I see... You there, you're pretty lucky. Seems like you got yourself a good item there, no?

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 1
voiceLines.subtitle: Welcome. Fufu, to think I would open up a shop like this... Oh, how ridiculous.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 2
voiceLines.subtitle: For you who has come from afar, welcome. Would you like some tea? Take your time and look around, I've got plenty in this shop. You might just find something you want.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 3
voiceLines.subtitle: I don't recommend holding back for too long. Either you release everything you bottled up, or you hold it for even longer... Don't be embarassed, if you have something that's troubling you, I will take a look for you here.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 4
voiceLines.subtitle: Thank you for your patronage.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 5
voiceLines.subtitle: When it comes to shops and business, I don't know anything really, but... since you come visit me so much, it might not be so bad. Please, come back again.

voiceLines.name: About the Shop 6
voiceLines.subtitle: Okay, time to exchange. Don't you drop it, okay? Here, come back again.

voiceLines.subtitle: For the prize exchange, you already finished everything to the last drop? Did you leave anything?
